citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/235340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F235340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=276d2d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴晚仲有人話放1500比我<br />\n但我前日600放比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c65ae79acd6191cf726339eb2478a77995f6aab","tid":644253,"uid":148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"買viagogo呢啲真係小心啲<br />\n試過買外國比賽睇 等到出發前都未收到電子飛email<br />\n出發前早幾個星期已經追緊viagogo個邊 <br />\n不過啲職員就hea鳩我話通常等到比賽前幾日先有都唔出奇<br />\n之後每隔幾日就email viagogo追飛<br />\n<br />\n到我出發一個星期都無消息 後尾忍唔住再打去屌viagogo先知賣家根本無原本嘅電子飛俾我<br />\n後尾viagogo話個賣家肯俾張同樣價位、同一行但唔同位置嘅實體飛寄俾我<br />\n但當時距離比賽開始得返3-4日 仲等佢寄都戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後決定唔要張飛 臨時買人地啲黃牛飛算 <br />\n仲要搞勁撚煩先肯退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f1db298d1f5a53b82ad566b5fdbb08d6ef1d55","tid":644253,"uid":92462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac9044c801f3fcd5642493f8afe1a50bad4ea70","tid":644253,"uid":157498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6d8198d22e8c4458878b91cef7ca395bae1d8f","tid":644253,"uid":97126,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"本身380一張<br />\n樓主張圖viagogo 880賣<br />\n仲叫正常價位?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:50:11.000